{"article_id":"eqS8bvDVJpLS5vj1","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump never ordered his coronavirus task force to slow down testing for the pathogen ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"key members told Congress on Tuesday .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"\" None of us have ever been told to slow down on testing .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"That just is a fact , \"","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Dr. Anthony Fauci , director of the National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases , testified before the House Energy and Commerce Committee .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"\" It ' s the opposite ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"we ' re going to be doing more testing , not less , \"","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Dr. Fauci said .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"One by one , the heads of the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention and the Food and Drug Administration and Brett Giroir , the country ' s testing \" czar , \" told lawmakers","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"they were not ordered by Mr. Trump to slow down diagnostic efforts .","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"\" The only way","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"that we will be able to understand","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"who has the disease ,","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"who is infected","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"and can pass it ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"to do appropriate contact tracing","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"is to test appropriately , smartly and as many people","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"as we can , \"","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"testified Adm. Giroir , an assistant health secretary and four-star admiral in the U.S. Public Health Service .","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"Mr. Trump ' s own remarks sparked the unusual round of questioning .","depth":3},{"id":20,"text":"He told a Tulsa rally","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"that testing is a double-edged sword","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"because","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"while it roots out cases ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"it also makes the country look bad","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"as large numbers of infections are posted on global tracking sites .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"He said","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"he told his people to \" slow the testing down , please . \"","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"His aides said","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"he was joking ,","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"though the president fanned the flames Tuesday","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"by saying :","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"\" I don ' t kid . \"","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"The U.S. is home to about 330 million people .","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"It has conducted over 25 million tests","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"and discovered over 2.3 million infections .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"More than 120,000 people in the U.S. have died from the disease ,","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"known as COVID-19 .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"Dr. Fauci said","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"America is looking at a \" mixed bag \" at this juncture in the pandemic .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"\" It ' s a serious situation .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"In some respects we ' ve done very well , \"","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"Dr. Fauci said ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"citing improvements in hard-hit New York City .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"\" In other areas of the country , we ' ve now seeing a disturbing surge of infections , \"","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"he added ,","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"citing flare-ups in Florida , Texas and Arizona .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"Mr. Trump headed to Arizona on Tuesday","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"to view a section of the border wall","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"and speak to conservative students in Phoenix .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Roughly 20 % of those tested in Arizona","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"are coming back positive ,","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"suggesting rampant spread","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"after the state reopened its economy .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"Dr. Fauci said","depth":4},{"id":55,"text":"states","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"seeing a spike","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"will need to devote manpower to testing and tracing cases ,","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"so they \" can do something about them . \"","depth":5},{"id":59,"text":"Governors","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"battered by new cases","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"say","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"many of the infections are hitting younger adults","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"who are unlikely to die from the disease .","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"Rep. Diana DeGette , Colorado Democrat , asked","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"whether people should link the declining death rate in the U.S. to that trend .","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"Dr. Fauci said","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"it ' s difficult to say ,","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"since deaths don ' t show up in the data","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"until weeks after cases are detected .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"\" I think","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"it ' s too early to make that kind of link , \"","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"Dr. Fauci said .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"\" Deaths always lag considerably behind cases . \"","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"the concern is people","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"involved in the localized spikes will infect other people ,","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"who might get sick","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"and die .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Committee Chairman Frank Pallone said","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"American testing the virus stumbled out of the gate","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"but appears to be improving .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"Still ,","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"he said","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"the country is short of 900,000 daily tests","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"experts say","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"it needs .","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"\" We are also hampered by the administration ' s refusal","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"to develop and implement a national testing and contact tracing strategy , \"","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"Mr. Pallone , New Jersey Democrat , said .","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"\" This can not continue","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"-","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"we need federal public health experts","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"to take more of a leadership role ,","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"and this administration is failing to allow that . \"","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"Adm. Giroir said","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"the U.S. should be able to conduct 40-50 million per month by fall .","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"test sites are required","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"to report demographic data ,","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"to ensure equitable access ,","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"and that Morehouse School of Medicine has been awarded $ 40 million for a three-year project","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"to deliver COVID-19 information to minority communities .","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"Prior to the testimony , Mr. Trump complained","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"that he didn ' t get the same amount of credit as his most famous task-force member .","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"\" We did a great job on CoronaVirus ,","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"including the very early ban on China , Ventilator production , and Testing ,","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"which is by far the most , and best , in the World .","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"We saved millions of U.S . lives. !","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"Yet the Fake News refuses to acknowledge this in a positive way , \"","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"he wrote in a series of tweets on his way to Arizona .","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"\" But they do give Dr. Anthony Fauci ,","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"who is with us in all ways ,","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"a very high 72 % Approval Rating .","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"So ,","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"if he is in charge along with V.P . etc. ,","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"and with us doing all of these really good things ,","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"why doesn ' t the Lamestream Media treat us","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"as they should ?","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"Answer :","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"Because they are Fake News ! \"","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":241,"left":153,"right":240,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":139,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":128,"right":138,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":122,"right":127,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":124,"right":126,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":124,"left":123,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":125,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":129,"right":137,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":137,"left":136,"right":18,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":134,"right":135,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":134,"left":10,"right":133,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":130,"right":132,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":130,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":132,"left":131,"right":15,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":135,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":19,"right":151,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"par